snippet.title: Corsairs : Conquest At Sea (GOLD) Gameplay
snippet.description:
A small gameplay video of "Corsairs Conquest at sea GOLD".
It was not easy but after a while i managed to record the gameplay :)
More gameplay videos will follow soon on my new channel! :)
Its running on Windows 7  PRO  64 bits
